hot men

00:00:05.682 --> 00:00:08.950
zeyer lang aroysgenumen di gantse zamd

00:00:10.626 --> 00:00:15.885
un hot dos geshotn im kerik in vagones, un m'hot dos avekgefirt.

00:00:16.262 --> 00:00:22.348
derbay iz geven oysgeboyt a, oyf tsu makhn dem dakh hot men shoyn

00:00:22.371 --> 00:00:25.335
di beton iz geven a

00:00:25.543 --> 00:00:28.827
zey hobn dos ongerufn a

00:00:29.577 --> 00:00:32.321
di shtub hobn zey ongerufn

00:00:34.302 --> 00:00:39.088
a, a be- a beton shtub, vos arbet oys beton. a fabrik vos arbet oys beton.

00:00:39.381 --> 00:00:43.121
un dos fleg geyn durkh breyte trubes derlangen oyfn barg

00:00:43.498 --> 00:00:44.724
ongisn

00:00:49.050 --> 00:00:51.047
un

00:00:51.047 --> 00:00:53.921
ot azoy hot men gegosn un gegosn yetst

00:00:54.113 --> 00:00:56.216
gegosn un gegosn

00:00:56.442 --> 00:01:00.368
biz vanet ven m'hot geendikt oysgisn hot men genumen aroysshepn di zamd.

00:01:01.082 --> 00:01:03.793
az m'hot aroysgeshept di gantse zamd

00:01:04.035 --> 00:01:06.273
iz geblibn ineveynik pust

00:01:07.174 --> 00:01:10.470
hobn zey ⟨aropgeshnitn⟩ di drotn ale vos s'iz do

00:01:10.470 --> 00:01:12.450
un m'hot gegrobn tifer

00:01:13.030 --> 00:01:17.918
un m'hot oysgeboyt, dos hobn mir nokh nit gezen dem ende

00:01:18.126 --> 00:01:24.257
mir hobn dos nit d- ni- nit dervart. gekumen bay tog eyn mol a

00:01:24.257 --> 00:01:25.995
Amerikaner SAMOLYOT

00:01:25.995 --> 00:01:29.224
un hot zikh avekgezetst oyfn dakh, fun barg oyf di beton.

00:01:30.377 --> 00:01:32.565
ikh hob gearbet yemolt

00:01:32.807 --> 00:01:35.028
bin ikh aribergegangen arbetn

00:01:35.220 --> 00:01:37.475
in a, dortn iz geven

00:01:37.937 --> 00:01:39.787
a tsement STUBE

00:01:40.502 --> 00:01:43.989
vu me flegt brengen vagones loyze tsement

00:01:44.940 --> 00:01:47.043
un dortn flegt men dos shitn

00:01:47.100 --> 00:01:50.059
un fun dortn flegt men derlangen dos in rern

00:01:50.059 --> 00:01:51.634
in di

00:01:51.707 --> 00:01:53.236
in beton fabrik.

00:01:54.323 --> 00:01:57.253
ikh hob gearbet baym oyslodn tsement

00:01:58.120 --> 00:01:59.396
in zeklekh.

00:02:00.853 --> 00:02:04.458
dortn iz geven a kolonen firer BUKANTS

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:10.939
BUKANTS iz geven in Kovne a bavuster fun di AVTOBUSn. er iz geven dortn a shutef.

00:02:12.312 --> 00:02:15.006
un a zun zayner iz dortn geven.

00:02:15.838 --> 00:02:16.726
a yid?

00:02:16.902 --> 00:02:17.920
a, a yid.

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:20.990
ye, er, neyn, neyn, neyn.

00:02:17.965 --> 00:02:20.321
er iz geven a kapo, vos UNK?

00:02:21.205 --> 00:02:22.903
azoy vi a brigadir.

00:02:24.462 --> 00:02:32.134
⟨im arayngef-⟩ un dortn hot gearbet mayn onkl, ot dos vos ikh hob aykh gevizn frier, dortn lebn mashin, az

00:02:32.173 --> 00:02:33.770
hobn mir dortn gearbet.

00:02:34.047 --> 00:02:38.681
di gantse arbet vos dortn iz geven, hot men gedarft oyslodn dem ovnt

00:02:38.805 --> 00:02:40.807
finf zeks vagones

00:02:40.813 --> 00:02:43.895
tsement. di kleyne vagones, di tsvelf tonike.

00:02:45.167 --> 00:02:50.527
di daytshn shteyen a gantsn ovnt, un me harget, me derlangt mit di nogaykes.

00:02:52.609 --> 00:02:56.045
az s'iz geven a UNK

00:02:57.013 --> 00:03:01.209
zog ikh tsu a daytshn, zog ikh "s'vert dir nit mies tsu shteyn un hargenen?"

00:03:03.460 --> 00:03:09.546
in dem iz ongekumen a STARSHIY leytenant, a kapitan fun di daytshn

00:03:10.412 --> 00:03:14.709
zogt er "vos hot ir geredt beyde tsvishn zikh?" UNK er fregt dem daytshn.

00:03:15.593 --> 00:03:20.382
zogt er "de- de- der yunger fregt far vos

00:03:20.382 --> 00:03:22.235
darf men hargenen?"

00:03:25.633 --> 00:03:27.939
zogt er tsu mir "kum aher.

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:30.690
vos leygstu for

00:03:31.489 --> 00:03:35.263
az me zol nit hargenen, un di arbet zol zayn fartik?"

00:03:38.087 --> 00:03:40.798
zog ikh "azoy vi mir arbetn toyg nit

00:03:41.091 --> 00:03:47.244
me darf nit ale mentshn geyn in eyn vagon un oyslodn eynem un nakher a tsveytn un nakher a dritn."

00:03:47.773 --> 00:03:52.222
zog ikh "eyner geyt aveket oystretn, dos iz a

00:03:52.836 --> 00:03:54.011
me dreyt zikh.

00:03:55.435 --> 00:03:58.416
un az s'kumt in der fri, kumt pinktlekh

00:03:58.607 --> 00:04:00.519
halb zeks a zeyger

00:04:00.519 --> 00:04:02.262
kumt der tsug

00:04:02.438 --> 00:04:05.739
tsunemen di vagones, darfn zey zayn reyn oysgekerte."

00:04:06.623 --> 00:04:10.363
zog ikh "me darf bashtimen in yedn vagon dray fir mentshn

00:04:12.445 --> 00:04:14.514
un di arbet vet zayn gemakht."

00:04:16.663 --> 00:04:19.812
zogt er "BUKANTS, kum aher.

00:04:22.452 --> 00:04:24.859
her oys" zogt er "vos der kleyner zogt."

00:04:26.518 --> 00:04:28.334
hot er mikh oykh oysgehert

00:04:30.973 --> 00:04:33.667
zogt er "ober zolst maskem zayn mit im

00:04:34.686 --> 00:04:37.785
un tomer di arbet vet nit zayn gemakht" zogt er

00:04:38.382 --> 00:04:40.046
"veln mir im hargenen."

00:04:42.938 --> 00:04:45.058
zaynen gekumen bay der arbet

00:04:46.296 --> 00:04:47.943
hob ikh gezogt azoy.

00:04:48.169 --> 00:04:50.930
"shtarkere dray man in a vagon.

00:04:51.156 --> 00:04:53.698
shvakhere fir man in a vagon.

00:04:55.054 --> 00:04:56.685
gor shtarke

00:04:56.691 --> 00:05:01.612
ts- tsvey man, un eynem a krankn, zolst ⟨im nor⟩ derlangen tsum hant."

00:05:04.167 --> 00:05:06.399
un mir hobn zikh avekgeshtelt

00:05:06.399 --> 00:05:08.042
dem ershtn tog

00:05:09.347 --> 00:05:14.201
un mir hobn undzer vagon geendikt tsvelf, halb eyns a zeyger bay nakht shoyn.

00:05:15.253 --> 00:05:18.757
un nokh hobn mir geendikt eyns, hot men geendikt halb tsvey.

00:05:18.865 --> 00:05:23.089
zaynen mir arayn in a vagon vu zey hobn a bisl zikh gedreyt

00:05:23.089 --> 00:05:26.925
oder take kranke mentshn. mir flegn trogn tsu dray zeklekh

00:05:27.201 --> 00:05:29.119
az zey flegn trogn tsu eynem.

00:05:30.154 --> 00:05:34.316
un der feler iz geven zeyerer vos zey flegn zikh farbindn di fis

00:05:34.322 --> 00:05:39.682
mit leydike zeklekh fun tsement mit drot, az zey fartshepenen un faln mitn zekl.

00:05:40.617 --> 00:05:43.125
hob ikh zey gezogt di papir aropnemen

00:05:43.806 --> 00:05:45.596
nit ⟨drey⟩ mit keyn drot

00:05:45.596 --> 00:05:48.526
es zol aykh nit fartshepenen, ir zolt nit faln

00:05:48.919 --> 00:05:52.001
un arbet azoy, zog ikh, vet aykh keyner nit hargenen.

00:05:53.307 --> 00:05:55.376
un azoy hobn mir zikh ayngearbet

00:05:55.753 --> 00:05:57.671
un m'hot gemakht di arbet

00:05:58.892 --> 00:06:02.176
nokh mi- mi- mit a sho gute frier.

00:06:03.043 --> 00:06:05.433
bin ikh tsugegangen tsu dem kapitan.

00:06:06.267 --> 00:06:08.185
zog ikh "kh'hob nokh a bite tsu dir."

00:06:09.304 --> 00:06:10.547
"vos vilstu?"

00:06:10.992 --> 00:06:12.707
zog ikh "do iz der bunker."

00:06:13.573 --> 00:06:17.198
ale hobn gevust fun bunker. in bunker iz geven heys

00:06:17.198 --> 00:06:18.174
a maykhl.

00:06:19.159 --> 00:06:23.287
⟨zolt mir⟩ antshuldikn, m'hot gekent dortn arayngeyn un zikh oysloyzn

00:06:23.344 --> 00:06:25.582
vayl di layz hot bay keynem nit gefelt.

00:06:30.094 --> 00:06:32.315
zog ikh "ven mir endikn di arbet

00:06:32.659 --> 00:06:37.530
arayngeyn zikh opruen a sho, onderhalbn, vifl, vifl tsayt es blaybt."

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.500
zogt der postn

00:06:40.894 --> 00:06:43.216
nemt aroys a papirl, shraybt onet

00:06:43.408 --> 00:06:46.490
tsu dortn, tsu dem glavnem fun, fun bunker

00:06:46.969 --> 00:06:48.768
az me zol undz araynlozn.

00:06:49.028 --> 00:06:54.456
un ot azoy flegt men undz araynlozn. m'hot undz shoyn gekent, flegn mir zikh dortn oysshlofn a dray sho.

00:06:55.677 --> 00:06:58.354
afile tsvey sho iz oykh geven genug tsu shlofn.

00:06:58.748 --> 00:07:02.657
az mir flegn kumen in geto iz bay daytshn iz do aza mode

00:07:02.983 --> 00:07:05.677
az m'vet dir nit khapn oyf nokh an arbet.

00:07:05.987 --> 00:07:07.398
az du vilst

00:07:07.708 --> 00:07:08.760
bite sheyn.

00:07:08.760 --> 00:07:09.829
ober

00:07:09.953 --> 00:07:11.350
dir tsvingen

00:07:11.350 --> 00:07:11.988
neyn.

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:15.684
fleg ikh in ge- in lager zikh gebn a drey

00:07:16.433 --> 00:07:22.716
fleg ikh tsuforn in zumer keler, flegt men forn brengen broyt, kartofl dortn, nokh farshidene zakhn

00:07:22.716 --> 00:07:25.449
UNK brekhst oyf di vinklen

00:07:25.449 --> 00:07:27.716
dervayle khapst a shtikl kroyt

00:07:28.093 --> 00:07:30.095
me ken zikh shoyn de- dreyen.

00:07:30.692 --> 00:07:34.837
dos hob ikh take gevolt fregn. vi iz geven mit esn dortn? m'hot aykh gegebn genug?

00:07:33.493 --> 00:07:36.575
o- fun onfang hot men gegebn esn

00:07:36.987 --> 00:07:38.753
⟨kolerley⟩ UNK ⟨gut⟩

00:07:39.467 --> 00:07:42.498
m'hot gegebn a lebl broyt a tog

00:07:42.555 --> 00:07:43.817
a daytshishn.

00:07:43.817 --> 00:07:47.594
di broyt iz geven lomir zogn fuftsik protsent polovines.

00:07:48.613 --> 00:07:49.856
dos iz NISHOVET.

00:07:50.841 --> 00:07:52.404
un

00:07:53.642 --> 00:07:56.690
me fleg gebn rayz kashe mit rozhinkes

00:07:58.317 --> 00:08:00.167
mit shitklekh shpek.

00:08:00.780 --> 00:08:05.954
m'hot zeyer gut gekormet. ober ⟨s'hot zikh⟩ genumen. yidn zaynen dokh yidn, azoy vi khazeyrim

00:08:06.433 --> 00:08:09.549
⟨s'hot zikh⟩ gevalgert a hoyfn geshimlte broyt.

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:15.337
zuntik az m'hot nit gearbet flegt men gebn onderhalbn leblekh broyt.

00:08:15.765 --> 00:08:17.058
nit arbetndik.

00:08:17.959 --> 00:08:21.530
geven oyf ⟨hoyf⟩ mit di, un nakher der front hot zikh dernentert

00:08:21.688 --> 00:08:26.115
hot men genumen shnaydn a lebl oyf dray, oyf tsvey

00:08:26.115 --> 00:08:28.199
nokh dem a lebl oyf dray

00:08:28.199 --> 00:08:30.173
nokh dem a lebl oyf fir

00:08:30.173 --> 00:08:32.921
nokh dem biz m'hot gegebn a moytskele broyt.

00:08:35.745 --> 00:08:37.426
ober alts eyns

00:08:37.888 --> 00:08:41.628
gut. mentshn zaynen geshtorbn fun hunger. mentshn zaynen geshtorbn

00:08:41.635 --> 00:08:44.413
vayle zey hobn nit gevelt arbetn.

00:08:44.571 --> 00:08:49.290
mayner a layblekher kuzin hot zikh ongeribn mit zalts di fis

00:08:49.768 --> 00:08:51.584
zol geyn di blut

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:54.369
zogt er "ober arbetn vel ikh nit."

00:08:54.966 --> 00:08:57.491
hot men im ibergeshikt in lager tsun

00:08:58.105 --> 00:09:01.924
me zogt az m'hot im gezen. er iz geblibn lebn

00:09:01.924 --> 00:09:07.060
ober f- ven zey zaynen gevorn hot men tsebombardirt dem POEZD un er iz umgekumen.

00:09:09.799 --> 00:09:12.273
azoy hobn mir zikh durkhgedreyt

00:09:12.448 --> 00:09:13.640
dem lager.

00:09:13.765 --> 00:09:17.404
s'iz geven eyn tsayt hot men gekrogn fun roytn kreyts

00:09:17.629 --> 00:09:18.939
pasilkes.

00:09:20.970 --> 00:09:25.604
un s'iz geven mit undz ungerishe yidn, a por hundert

00:09:25.915 --> 00:09:29.925
di ungerishe yidn flegn di ershte tsayt krign briv fun der heym

00:09:30.842 --> 00:09:32.996
un zey flegn krign peklekh.

00:09:35.230 --> 00:09:43.943
un zey hobn zikh azoy getsoygn, ober vos, mit zey hot zikh keyner nit gekent oyfreydn, vayle zey hobn nor di MAGYARish geredt, az zey hobn nit keyn daytsh

00:09:43.943 --> 00:09:48.352
nit keyn rusish, nit keyn poylish, nit keyn yidish, keyn shprakh nit gekent.

00:09:49.017 --> 00:09:53.297
nokh dem hot men gebrakht tsvey hundert khevre poylishe

00:09:53.893 --> 00:09:54.933
Vilner.

00:09:56.577 --> 00:09:58.776
iz geven eyner Burshteynke

00:09:58.776 --> 00:10:00.857
oykhet fun di zelbe khevre

00:10:02.280 --> 00:10:05.463
un er hot ale tsvey hundert oysgeharget.

00:10:05.537 --> 00:10:07.235
er, nit der daytsh.

00:10:06.735 --> 00:10:07.724
far vos?

00:10:08.102 --> 00:10:09.513
azoy hot er gevelt.

00:10:09.486 --> 00:10:10.326
a yid?

00:10:10.279 --> 00:10:10.981
a yid.

00:10:10.326 --> 00:10:12.596
a- fun, fun di Vilner?

00:10:12.596 --> 00:10:14.323
eyner fun di Vilner oder vo-

00:10:14.498 --> 00:10:17.158
fun vanet er hot geshtamt veys ikh nit.

00:10:19.071 --> 00:10:24.465
az m'hot zikh bafrayt veys ikh az m'hot zikh nokh im geyogt iber di dekher. er iz gelofn. m'hot im gekhapt

00:10:24.623 --> 00:10:27.418
un m'hot im geSUDevet un m'hot im derharget.

00:10:26.918 --> 00:10:29.940
vos far a postn hot er gehat dortn UNK?

00:10:29.162 --> 00:10:34.120
er iz geven azoy a blok eltester faktish.

00:10:30.564 --> 00:10:31.724
a kapo?

00:10:32.690 --> 00:10:34.219
a blok el-

00:10:34.410 --> 00:10:38.184
ts- m'hot oyf zey oysgeshosn, oder vi ar- vi arum hot ⟨dos⟩ zey oysgeharget?

00:10:37.280 --> 00:10:40.500
neyn, ha- hargenen.

00:10:38.275 --> 00:10:40.732
geshlo- ah, geshlogn.

00:10:40.500 --> 00:10:44.225
geshlogn, er hot gekent itster krign dem kesele mit di esn

00:10:44.383 --> 00:10:47.330
flegt er tsugeyn im gebn a zets, UNK oysgisn di esn.

00:10:48.197 --> 00:10:50.165
a sadist, stam a sad-

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:52.697
ikh hob im a mol tsugedint

00:10:52.787 --> 00:10:55.565
az er hot gekhapt finf un tsvantsik shmits

00:10:56.736 --> 00:10:59.885
UNK fregn, "vi azoy? vi, vi bistu geven a kluger?"

00:11:00.415 --> 00:11:07.025
bay mir di klumpes hobn zikh aropgetrogn, m- mit di shikh undzere geven shtof oybn un untn he- holts

00:11:07.025 --> 00:11:08.885
hot dos geheysn klumpes.

00:11:11.788 --> 00:11:16.321
zog ikh, iz az du host gedarft for zikh ven vegn farrikhtn a zakh

00:11:16.665 --> 00:11:20.700
iz geven dortn a varshtat ⟨in⟩ vos mentshn zaynen gezesn un farrikht

00:11:20.985 --> 00:11:22.290
der Burshteyn

00:11:22.290 --> 00:11:24.844
di klumpes mayne, ikh ken nit geyn.

00:11:25.508 --> 00:11:27.156
hot er zey tsugenumen

00:11:29.524 --> 00:11:31.290
un er hot avekgetrogn

00:11:31.414 --> 00:11:34.513
ober er hot mir zey nit gebrakht tsu der tsayt kerik.

00:11:35.413 --> 00:11:38.174
in der fri iz geven a apel

00:11:38.687 --> 00:11:40.503
dos ven me tseylt di mentshn

00:11:42.197 --> 00:11:45.245
hob ikh genumen, mir zaynen geven in aza min barak

00:11:45.792 --> 00:11:47.119
un do shloft men.

00:11:47.175 --> 00:11:49.632
un ikh hob zikh avekgeleygt untern dekhl.

00:11:50.888 --> 00:11:53.143
m'efnt di tir. keyner zet zikh nit.

00:11:53.183 --> 00:11:54.392
me geyt avek.

00:11:55.275 --> 00:11:58.374
iber a sho hot men getseylt, un es felt a mentsh

00:12:00.169 --> 00:12:04.635
biz vanet iz geven der lager firer iz geven KIRSCH

00:12:07.527 --> 00:12:10.552
er aleyn iz gegangen kukn iber di barakes.

00:12:10.552 --> 00:12:13.055
az er iz gegangen hob ikh zikh avekgezetst

00:12:13.332 --> 00:12:15.520
ikh bin shoyn UNK gelegn un gezesn

00:12:17.719 --> 00:12:19.839
un er hot ibergetseylt. s'shtimt.

00:12:21.685 --> 00:12:25.054
zogt er "vu WARST DU frier? vu bistu geven frier?"

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:27.602
zog ikh az "do zits ikh di gantse tsayt."

00:12:29.802 --> 00:12:32.175
"far vos bist nit aroys oyfn apel?"

00:12:33.514 --> 00:12:39.277
iz Burshteyn hot gehat rekht dir tsu lozn ineveynik, ober er hot gedarft meldn az bay im iz do a mentsh.

00:12:40.348 --> 00:12:43.919
zog ikh "kh'hob avekgegebn mayne klumpn Burshteynen."

00:12:46.828 --> 00:12:50.939
gut. m'hot mir gebrakht a por klumpn. ikh bin aroys. m'hot ibergetseylt. s'shtimt.

00:12:51.891 --> 00:12:54.028
itster hot men genumen zukhn

00:12:54.068 --> 00:12:56.762
⟨iz⟩ dortn geven eyner a bashuldikter.

00:12:57.915 --> 00:13:02.313
hot men gegebn Burshteynen, hot er gegebn, er zol im shmaysn.

00:13:03.484 --> 00:13:05.941
tsvantsik, finf un tsvantsik shmits.

00:13:07.483 --> 00:13:11.949
az er hot im geshmisn, hot er im opgeshmisn epes biz akhtsn, biz vifl

00:13:12.242 --> 00:13:13.923
zogt der KIRSCH

00:13:14.908 --> 00:13:15.779
"halt.

00:13:16.512 --> 00:13:18.058
du heyb zikh oyf."

00:13:18.418 --> 00:13:22.681
zogt er "Burshteyn, tsi arop di hoyzn. ikh vel dir vayzn vi me darf shmaysn."

00:13:22.789 --> 00:13:25.989
un er hot im arayngehakt finf un tsvantsik gantse.

00:13:28.999 --> 00:13:31.119
er fleg kenen dir makhn

00:13:31.328 --> 00:13:32.520
az

