un ikh hob zikh mit im derredt

00:27:26.353 --> 00:27:31.831
az me ⟨zol⟩ n- nit oysshisn un er vet krign fun aykh a shayn tsu forn aheym

00:27:32.040 --> 00:27:34.315
ruik, me shenkt im dem lebn

00:27:34.315 --> 00:27:35.257
derfar

00:27:36.090 --> 00:27:40.252
un zey hobn aroysgenumen a shrayb mashinke fun tank

00:27:40.528 --> 00:27:45.798
un zey hobn dos altsding oysgeshribn. m'hot im gegebn a shayn; m'hot im nokhge-

00:27:45.798 --> 00:27:46.732
gerat

00:27:46.907 --> 00:27:53.097
arayngeyn in a shtibl un gefinen zakhn oyf zayn mos, er zol zikh onton in tsivile zakhn

00:27:53.097 --> 00:27:56.030
un ver s'vet im nit opshteln, zol er vayzn dem shayn

00:27:56.965 --> 00:27:57.819
UNK

00:27:58.078 --> 00:27:59.996
zol er vayzn zayn shayn.

00:28:01.420 --> 00:28:02.865
azoy iz geven

00:28:02.989 --> 00:28:04.839
un der daytsh iz avek

00:28:04.963 --> 00:28:05.936
fun undz.

00:28:06.280 --> 00:28:07.826
itster, di nakht

00:28:07.832 --> 00:28:11.454
fun ershtn oyfn tsveytn may iz geven aza min shney

00:28:12.102 --> 00:28:15.977
az ⟨zaynen⟩ geblibn in vald untern shney

00:28:16.388 --> 00:28:21.444
toyznter, toyznter mentshn, vayle s'iz geven shney mistome onderhalbn meter di heykh.

00:28:26.125 --> 00:28:28.937
iz az ikh hob zikh gedreyt arum fayer

00:28:29.348 --> 00:28:32.260
iz mir dos di erd shoyn nit farshotn.

00:28:39.591 --> 00:28:40.969
nokh dem

00:28:41.599 --> 00:28:43.938
hot men genumen ver vu loyfn.

00:28:44.721 --> 00:28:51.515
eyner iz gelofn in di shtibl. eyner iz gelofn in di shtibl. dortn ⟨iz nor⟩ geven azoy fil shtiblekh far azoy fil mentshn arayntsugeyn.

00:28:52.534 --> 00:28:55.666
bay undz hot zikh gefunen eyner, ⟨Fole⟩ Glukh.

00:28:56.719 --> 00:28:59.109
er hot gelebt in Vilne UNK olevasholem.

00:28:59.892 --> 00:29:01.793
do iz er geshtorbn in land.

00:29:03.486 --> 00:29:09.251
⟨ot aza⟩ guter mekhaniker shofer, un er hot ⟨sheyn⟩ tsuzamengepurket a mashin

00:29:09.713 --> 00:29:16.963
un ikh hob zikh oykh aroyfgekhapt oyf dem mashin, un mir zaynen avekgeforn nenter tsu di Alpn, mistomen a fuftsn tsvantsik kilometer.

00:29:18.201 --> 00:29:24.337
a daytsh hot undz untergezogt az dortn iz do a restoran vu di daytshn esn tsvey a zeyger mitog.

00:29:25.204 --> 00:29:30.783
un mir zaynen derforn dortn, ⟨un m'iz⟩ arayn, dokh azoy vi a pogrom hot men gemakht

00:29:32.173 --> 00:29:35.069
iz gekumen der balebos an italyener

00:29:35.430 --> 00:29:39.254
zogt er "zetst zikh ale bay di tishn. ale veln vern badint

00:29:39.345 --> 00:29:42.261
un krign di shenste un di beste esn."
